steps.name: I check that the "Welcome Screen" is displayed

I check that the "First SignIn Screen" is displayed
I click on "SKIP" button

I click on "CONTINUE" button

I click on "CONTINUE" button
I skip linking my card
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I mock the location of the device to "DENMARK_10888" as guest user
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I check that "SIGN IN OR SIGN UP" button is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "DENMARK_10888" station

I enter the site ID "DENMARK_10888" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "CLOSE" button
I check that "SIGN IN OR SIGN UP" button is displayed
I click on "STORES" button
I check that the "Stores Screen" is displayed
I click on "USER LOCATION" button
I click on "VIEW LIST/MAP" button
I check that the "Station List Screen" is displayed
I scroll DOWN to the station ID '11101' and click on the 'STORE DETAILS' button
I check that the "Stores Details Back Button" is displayed
I check that the 'SERVICES' header is displayed
I click on "Back button" CTA Store Details Page
I scroll UP to the station ID '19988' and click on the 'STORE DETAILS' button
I check that the "Stores Details Back Button" is displayed
I get all visible available service types
I check that the actual value: "1" is greater or equal than value "1"
I click on "Back button" CTA Store Details Page
I scroll DOWN to the station ID '10133' and click on the 'STORE DETAILS' button
I check that the "Stores Details Back Button" is displayed
I get all visible available service types
I check that the actual value: "12" is greater or equal than value "5"
I click on "Back button" CTA Store Details Page
